     C* E1: F-spec cols 71-72 external file conditioning (U1-U8),
     C* output side. CONDOUT is unconditioned and gets its line;
     C* CONDOUT2 is conditioned on U2 (default off) and must get
     C* NO output line at all, despite an unconditioned O-spec.
     FPFDATA  IP  F    80              DISK
     FCONDOUT O   F    132             PRINTER
     FCONDOUT2O   F    132             PRINTER                        U2
     IPFDATA  AA
     I                                     1   1   0DUMMY
     OCONDOUT D  1
     O                                 10   'YES'
     OCONDOUT2D  1
     O                                 10   'ALSO'
